data.description: EVERYTHING'S BIGGER IN TEXAS & this home is no exception!  The primary bedroom with ensuite bath, & a guest bedroom & second full bath are on the main level, as well as a second dining or living room, breakfast area, & large family room w electric fireplace that looks out on the spacious backyard deck & outdoor kitchen.  Upstairs, you'll find a large game room, two more bedrooms, a full bath, & a huge room that is multi-functional.  With a built in loft that expands the width of the room, this could be an incredible playroom for kids, an ideal bedroom for an older teen w room for a sofa, a family media room, dance studio, or whatever your mind can conceive.  Mounted TVs stay!  Appliances stay, which includes the electric range, kitchen refrigerator, washer & dryer, & garage refrigerator & freezer. New flooring has been installed throughout the house in the past year. Dual water heaters & AC units. 10x20 Shed w Electric. Custom storage & more!
